    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo xanc<lb break="no" n="2"/>to <note>sic</note> Mercu<lb break="no" n="3"/>rio <expan><abbr>Prisc</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan><lb break="no" n="4"/>nius Sed<lb break="no" n="5"/>ulius <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex cert="low">olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex cert="low">ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex cert="low">aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In zwei Teile gebrochen. Z. 4: Buchstabe E in Form von II geschrieben. Z. 3-6: möglicherweise auch zwei Personen: Prisc(i)/nius (et) Sed/ulius v(otum) / s(olverunt) l(ibentes) l(aeti) m(erito).</p>
            </div>
